('Rajae Amrani', 'Capgemini', 'Balancing work and studies was challenging but incredibly rewarding. The professional experience I gained was invaluable, and my company became my first employer.', 'Alternance', 2),
('Hassan Zouaki', 'Maroc Telecom', 'The Alternance program provided the perfect balance between academic learning and professional practice. I felt fully prepared for the workforce.', 'Alternance', 3);